OL,3,C"There's no way to describe the pain"
OL,4,C- Parents of toddler who died at
OL,5,Cnursery
OL,7,FThe parents of a 14-month-old boy who
OL,8,Fdied after being suffocated at a
OL,9,Fnursery in Dudley have said they
OL,10,F"cannot comprehend" the way he was
OL,11,Ftreated.
OL,13,FNoah Sibanda was held face down while
OL,14,Fstaff at Fairytales Day Nursery in
OL,15,FBourne Street in Dudley were trying to
OL,16,Fget him to go to sleep.
OL,18,FCCTV shows Kimberley Cookson, 23,
OL,19,Ftightly wrapping Noah in a sleeping
OL,20,Fbag, placing a blanket over his head
OL,21,Fand lying him face down on a cushion.
OL,26,@kD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
