OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776456351
OL,3,C"There's no way to describe the pain"
OL,4,C- Parents of toddler who died at
OL,5,Cnursery
OL,7,FThe 23-year-old, from Dudley, also
OL,8,Frestrained him with her left leg
OL,9,Fbefore Noah went unchecked for two
OL,10,Fhours on December 9th, 2022.
OL,12,FHe was then found unresponsive in the
OL,13,Fbaby room at the nursery and was
OL,14,Fpronounced dead in hospital an hour
OL,15,Flater despite efforts to revive him.
OL,17,FCookson was jailed for three years and
OL,18,Ffour months at Wolverhampton Crown
OL,19,FCourt today for his death.
OL,26,@kD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776456351
OL,3,C"There's no way to describe the pain"
OL,4,C- Parents of toddler who died at
OL,5,Cnursery
OL,7,FNoah's parents, Masi and Thulani,
OL,8,Fappeared outside court after the
OL,9,Fsentencing alongside senior
OL,10,Finvestigating officer Detective
OL,11,FInspector Carla Thompson, who read a
OL,12,Fstatement on their behalf.
OL,14,FIt said: "Our son Noah died at just 14
OL,15,Fmonths because of the gross negligence
OL,16,Fof someone who was trusted to care for
OL,17,Fhim.
OL,26,@kD@AOUvD@JOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776456351
OL,3,C"There's no way to describe the pain"
OL,4,C- Parents of toddler who died at
OL,5,Cnursery
OL,7,F"There is no way to describe the depth
OL,8,Fof pain that comes from losing a
OL,9,Fchild, and there is no form of justice
OL,10,Fthat can ever balance what has been
OL,11,Ftaken from us."
OL,13,FThe statement added: "We cannot
OL,14,Fcomprehend what could justify treating
OL,15,Fa barely walking child the way Noah
OL,16,Fwas treated.
OL,26,@kD@AOUoD@AOUsD@OO]uD@VOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776456351
OL,3,C"There's no way to describe the pain"
OL,4,C- Parents of toddler who died at
OL,5,Cnursery
OL,7,F"There's no sentence that would amount
OL,8,Fto the pain and suffering Noah was
OL,9,Fcaused, or the suffering that has
OL,10,Fspread to everyone who loved him.
OL,11,FNothing can restore what's been taken
OL,12,Ffrom us."
OL,14,FNursery owner Deborah Latewood has
OL,15,Fadmitted a Health and Safety at Work
OL,16,FAct offence on the basis that she did
OL,17,Fnot know children were being put down
OL,18,Fto sleep in a dangerous way, but
OL,19,Fshould have known, while the firm
OL,20,Fwhich ran the nursery has admitted
OL,21,Fcorporate manslaughter.
OL,26,@kD@AOUoD@AOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776456351
OL,3,C"There's no way to describe the pain"
OL,4,C- Parents of toddler who died at
OL,5,Cnursery
OL,7,FThe 55-year-old was given a six-month
OL,8,Fjail sentence, suspended for two years.
OL,10,FThe judge, Mr Justice Choudhary, said
OL,11,Fhe would "ordinarily" have sentenced
OL,12,FLatewood to immediate custody, but a
OL,13,Fchange made under the 2026 Sentencing
OL,14,FAct meant any sentence under 12 months
OL,15,Fmust be suspended.
OL,17,FThe judge fined Fairytales Day Nursery
OL,18,F#240,000 for corporate manslaughter,
OL,19,Fnoting that the risk of death had been
OL,20,F"highly foreseeable".
OL,26,@kD@AOUsD@JOUsD@UO]|D@AOU|D@TO]
